symc.name: DUPLICATE_CLOSE_SOURCE
symc.desc: Closes the source handle. This occurs regardless of any error status returned.

symc.name: DUPLICATE_SAME_ACCESS
symc.desc: Ignores the dwDesiredAccess parameter. The duplicate handle has the same access as the source handle.
